title: When I press launch button, makes sound but does absolutely nothing.
body:
This only happens on my laptop, not my desktop. 
I open league, shows the launcher window, I press launch, the sound plays, but nothing happens -> the window stays the same. 
I've attempted to repair League, but that also doesn't do anything. I've uninstalled and reinstalled. Same effect. 
Help would be greatly appreciated.

replies.body: Yeah I am. Figured it out haha

I am using Bitdefender total security 2015, I've had this problem for over a week as well, I came back from overseas to a new patch and couldn't get past launch screen. I've noticed it works in Windows safe mode though, after accepting the eula and tou through safe mode, it then sometimes lets me get to the login screen after a tiny wait.
I have the same problem, a fix plz riot?
Did you ever find a fix for this? Been at it for 2 days with no luck.
Disabling bitdefender worked for me. just on startup, thats if you use bitdefender
